<article class="marketing">

  <section class="marketing-section marketing-section--intro">
    <header class="marketing-section-header">
      <p class="marketing-section-header-leadin">Partner with Changelog Media</p>
      <h1>We reach 85,000 developers weekly</h1>
      <p>350,000 monthly listens&nbsp;&nbsp;•&nbsp;&nbsp;<%= @weekly |> NewsletterView.subscribers(:all, 9786) |> SharedHelpers.comma_separated %> email subscribers&nbsp;&nbsp;•&nbsp;&nbsp;250,000 monthly pageviews</p>

      <div class="marketing-button_group" style="--max-width-group: 380px;">
        <%= link "Get in touch", to: "mailto:adam@changelog.com", class: "button_large button_large--default" %>
        <%= link "Pricing", to: Routes.page_path(@conn, :sponsor_pricing), class: "button_large button_large--default" %>
      </div>
      <p class="button_note">Or call us at 888-974-CHLG (2454)</p>
    </header>
  </section>

  <section class="marketing-section">
    <header class="marketing-section-header">
      <h3>Slow &amp; steady wins</h3>
      <h2>Loved by brands, trusted by developers</h2>
      <p>Every day we influence developers at some of the most innovative tech companies in the world. We speak to the builders, leaders, and planners defining the future of software.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="marketing-section-proof">
      <img src='<%= Routes.static_url(@conn, "/images/content/marketing/render-color--on-dark.svg") %>' alt="Render" class="proof-logo" style="max-width: 150px">
      <p class="proof-quote">The value we get from each interaction with Adam Stacoviak (and team) is tremendous. When we talk through goals, ideas, and strategies it's like he's a member of the Render team &mdash; giving every idea he has to help us find ways to truely connect with the developer community.</p>
      <%= for example <- Changelog.SponsorStyle.render() do %>
      <%= render(SharedView, "_mini_player.html", title: example.name, audio: example.audio, duration: example.duration, theme: "dark") %>
      <% end %>
      <img src='<%= Routes.static_url(@conn, "/images/content/marketing/anurag-goel.jpg") %>' alt="Anurag Goel" class="proof-avatar">
      <p class="proof-title-line-1">Anurag Goel</p>
      <p class="proof-title-line-2">Founder and CEO of Render</p>
    </div>

    <div class="marketing-section-wrap marketing-content text-center">
      <p>Trusted by these brands to share their story with developers.</p>
    </div>

    <%= render("_logo_grid--dark.html", assigns) %>

    <%= render("_footer_section.html", conn: @conn) %>
  </section>

  <section class="marketing-section marketing-section--grey">
    <a id="how-it-works" class="anchor"></a>
    <header class="marketing-section-header">
      <h3>Facts tell, stories sell</h3>
      <h2>Connect authentically with developers</h2>
      <p>The primary challenge for brands we work with is being able to authentically communicate their value to developers. It's about more than just telling developers who you are and what you do. What's your story? Why should they give you their attention? We focus on defining and communicating a narrative that informs, entertains, and educates what you bring to the market.</p>
      <p><%= link "Listen to ad styles we support", to: Routes.page_path(@conn, :sponsor_styles), class: "action-link" %></p>
    </header>

    <div class="marketing-section-proof">
      <img src='<%= Routes.static_url(@conn, "/images/content/marketing/sourcegraph-color--on-dark.svg") %>' alt="Sourcegraph" class="proof-logo" style="max-width: 240px">
      <p class="proof-quote">Developers listen to podcasts to learn new things. Podcasts are the perfect medium for us to <em>consistently communicate</em> our value to developers all over the world. Changelog has a proven process to discover our goals to form a strategy that gets results. They know their audience <em>very well</em>. They've helped us shape and tell our story in an authentic way.</p>
      <%= for example <- Changelog.SponsorStyle.sourcegraph() do %>
      <%= render(SharedView, "_mini_player.html", title: example.name, audio: example.audio, duration: example.duration, theme: "dark") %>
      <% end %>
      <img src='<%= Routes.static_url(@conn, "/images/content/marketing/beyang-liu.jpg") %>' alt="Beyang Liu" class="proof-avatar">
      <p class="proof-title-line-1">Beyang Liu</p>
      <p class="proof-title-line-2">Co-founder and CTO of Sourcegraph</p>
    </div>

